{"id":"a584def0-2470-49a6-915c-c99635a75ad6","name":"Mejiro Ardan (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/IlzqCYxoT6HAiJx7o4YO0.webp\" style=\"width: 457px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>⋄⋄⋄ 🔹 ⋄⋄⋄</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>She wants to shine bright, no matter how briefly! This well-to-do girl has legs of glass.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A sheltered young lady—ephemeral, gentle, and thoughtful. Despite her fragile, \"glass\" legs putting her at a disadvantage when running, she refuses to let cynicism keep her down. As a child, her frail body kept her from most recreation and social activities, so she finds community life at the academy to be quite the novel experience.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><br><em>\"History may be recounted later as one likes, yet I choose to shine in the here and now.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WLVQyxW3S5k0lFLrYa8TR.webp\" style=\"width: 461px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">❋ ⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄ ❋</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><br><em>1) Fatigue</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><em>2) Bandage</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><em>3) Chinese grocery store</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><em>4) Invitation</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><em>5) Hotspring</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 206, 210);\"><strong><em>6) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HIH-NcFkhYh4oZLJ6M5-C.webp\" style=\"width: 528px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">❋ ⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄ ❋</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Another Mejiro done.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Go win her some races, she deserves them.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">By the way, i might also be releasing those 2 Umamusumes sooner than expeceted.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/uG-jTOlVvpWzw2kBsS98w.webp\" style=\"width: 315px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">(God i love the two of them)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Day 15 of posting songs that i like.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3Tg8JctqoeIwZ3Rue8BjaI?si=5530ac8311f24bf1\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Ratamahatta - Sepultura</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4w-owJ75mC9FZEpoFsm7L.webp\" style=\"width: 308px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">❋ ⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄⋄ ❋</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/110003829\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/JDanboru1182/status/1740209655559921943/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@JDanboru</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\